name: Disappointed, angry, and ashamed
description:
"disappointed, angry, and ashamed"
this is what I felt right now, this is the way I interpret myself as an artist that felt down whenever I see my own drawing art...

the thing is, this is what makes me feels there are burning spirit inside my own that says "you gotta improve yourself, or you be left out"

But the feel of disgusts and ashamed are still throat down on me, yet I could only feel the air in the void...

Through fortune, fame & flame I burn. the only thing that I could do as an artist is to express myself on a blank canvas

each stroke each color represents the emotion, the disgust, anger, disappointment, and shame toward self...
